author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Vente-Unique.Com SA Says Midcap Partners Partially Exercised Overallotment Option Resulting In Issue Of Additional 365,015 Shares
text:
Vente-Unique.Com SA:
* SAYS MIDCAP PARTNERS PARTIALLY EXERCISED OVERALLOTMENT OPTION RESULTING IN ISSUE OF ADDITIONAL 365,015 SHARES
* PLACEMENT OF 365,015 ADDITIONAL SHARES AT OFFER PRICE OF € 10.70/SHARE, FOR AMOUNT OF € 3,905,660.50 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
